      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="etf-comparison">
      <h2>4. Comparing the Giants: VOO vs. IVV vs. SPY</h2>
      <p>While they all track the exact same 500 companies, there are subtle differences between the three major ETFs.</p>

      <div class="comparison-table-wrapper">
        <table class="comparison-table">
